{"tid":155461,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[Netflix]鐵拳俠劣評如潮。主角：最衰特朗普","createTime":"2017-03-14T05:14:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-14T07:49:20.000Z","uid":60341,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"290fc785c8638e9e621b9cbcbc80089c2b4336b0","tid":155461,"uid":60341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T05:14:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.thewrap.com/finn-jones-iron-fist-reviews-donald-trump/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thewrap.com%2Ffinn-jones-iron-fist-reviews-donald-trump%2F&d=uCl2s%2BJteilWOEmp%2BZl8kb%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=3b3b5d43\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.thewrap.com/finn-jones-iron-fist-reviews-donald-trump/</a><br />\n<br />\nSpeaking to Radio Times, Jones said part of the problem is that his &ldquo;Iron Fist&rdquo; character, Danny Rand, is a white billionaire. And as he sees it, the one of those currently holding the US presidency is making critics less receptive to Danny&rsquo;s story.<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;I think the world has changed a lot since we were filming that television show,&rdquo; he said in the interview. &ldquo;<span style=\"color: red;\">I&rsquo;m playing a white American billionaire superhero, at a time when the white American billionaire archetype is public enemy number one, especially in the US</span>.<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;We filmed the show way before Trump&rsquo;s election, and I think it&rsquo;s very interesting to see how that perception, now that Trump&rsquo;s in power, how it makes it very difficult to root for someone coming from white privilege, when that archetype is public enemy number one.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n大意：因為白人億萬富翁Donald Trump變成全美公敵，連帶所有有錢白人嘅社會觀感下滑。導致觀眾唔中意同為有錢白人嘅主角。<br />\n<br />\n屙屎唔出瀨地硬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"269a36bdda09b1a7225bff608e759832f5386bee","tid":155461,"uid":86587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T05:15:47.00